## <a name="france-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4707">Номер страховки для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4707">France health insurance number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4708">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4708">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4709">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4709">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4710">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4710">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4711">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4711">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4712">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4712">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4713">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4713">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4714">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4714">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4715">21 цифра цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4715">21 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4716">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4716">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4717">21 цифра:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4717">21 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4718">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4718">ten digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4719">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4719">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4720">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4720">ten digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4721">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4721">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4722">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4722">a digit</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4723">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4723">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4724">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4724">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4725">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4725">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4726">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4726">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4727">регулярное выражение Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4727">the regex Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4728">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4728">a keyword from Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="9bc2069e-76df-4ff9-ac02-2f519469e236" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4729">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4729">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_france_health_insurance_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4730">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4730">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4731">Карточка страхования</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4731">insurance card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4732">Витале корзины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4732">carte vitale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4733">Корзина д'ассурé социальных сетей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4733">carte d'assuré social</span></span>


## <a name="france-national-id-card-cni"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4734">Национальный идентификационный номер страны Франции (CNI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4734">France national id card (CNI)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4735">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4735">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4736">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4736">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4737">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4737">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4738">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4738">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4739">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4739">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4740">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4740">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4741">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4741">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4742">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4742">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4743">регулярное выражение Regex_france_cni находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4743">The regular expression Regex_france_cni finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4744">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4744">A keyword from Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France CNI -->
    <Entity id="f741ac74-1bc0-4665-b69b-f0c7f927c0c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="65">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_france_cni" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4745">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4745">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_france_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4746">Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4746">Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4747">card number

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4751">CNI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4751">cni</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4752">Компте банкаире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4752">compte bancaire</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4753">Национальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4753">national identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4754">Национальная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4754">national identity</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4755">натионалидно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4755">nationalidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4756">нумéро д'ассуранце маладие</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4756">numéro d'assurance maladie</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4757">нумéро де корзина Витале</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4757">numéro de carte vitale</span></span>

   
## <a name="france-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4758">Номер паспорта для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4758">France passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4759">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4759">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4760">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4760">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4761">девять цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4761">nine digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4762">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4762">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4763">девять цифр и букв:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4763">nine digits and letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4764">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4764">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4765">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4765">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4766">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4766">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4767">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4767">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4768">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4768">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4769">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4769">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4770">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4770">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4771">функция Func_fr_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4771">The function Func_fr_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4772">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4772">A keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France Passport Number -->
<Entity id="3008b884-8c8c-4cd8-a289-99f34fc7ff5d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4773">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4773">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4774">Keyword_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4774">Keyword_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4775">Passport Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4775">Passport Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4776">Passport No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4776">Passport No</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4777">Passport#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4777">Passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4778">Службу #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4778">Passport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4779">пасспортид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4779">PassportID</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4780">пасспортно</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4780">Passportno</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4781">пасспортнумбер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4781">passportnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4782">パスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4782">パスポート</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4783">パスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4783">パスポート番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4784">パスポートのнум</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4784">パスポートのNum</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4785">パスポート＃</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4785">パスポート ＃</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4786">Numéro de passeport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4786">Numéro de passeport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4787">Passeport n °</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4787">Passeport n °</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4788">Passeport Non</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4788">Passeport Non</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4789">Passeport#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4789">Passeport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4790">пассепорт #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4790">Passeport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4791">пассепортнон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4791">PasseportNon</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4792">Passeportn °</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4792">Passeportn °</span></span>

      
## <a name="france-social-security-number-insee-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4793">Номер социального страхования для Франции (INSEE) или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4793">France social security number (INSEE) or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4794">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в номер социального страхования ЕС и эквивалентный тип конфиденциальной информации и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4794">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Social Security Number and Equivalent ID sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4795">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4795">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4796">15 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4796">15 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4797">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4797">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4798">Должен соответствовать одному из двух шаблонов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4798">Must match one of two patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4799">13 цифр, за которыми следует пробел, за которым следуют две цифры.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4799">13 digits followed by a space followed by two digits</span></span><br/>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4800">или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4800">or</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4801">15 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4801">15 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4802">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4802">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4803">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4803">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4804">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4804">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4805">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 95 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4805">A DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4806">Функция Func_french_insee или Func_fr_insee находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4806">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4807">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_fr_insee;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4807">A keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4808">контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4808">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4809">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4809">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4810">Функция Func_french_insee или Func_fr_insee находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4810">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4811">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_fr_insee не находится;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4811">No keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4812">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4812">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France INSEE -->
<Entity id="71f62b97-efe0-4aa1-aa49-e14de253619d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Func_fr_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Func_fr_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4813">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4813">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_fr_insee"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4814">Keyword_fr_insee</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4814">Keyword_fr_insee</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4815">INSEE</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4815">insee</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4818">national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4818">national id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4822">Нет.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4822">no.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4823">д'идентитé</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4823">d'identité</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4824">numero d'identite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4824">numero d'identite</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4825">no d'identite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4825">no d'identite</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4826">Нет.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4826">no.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4827">д'идентите</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4827">d'identite</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4828">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4828">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4829">social security code</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4829">social security code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4832">d'identité nationale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4832">d'identité nationale</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4835">numéro d'assurance sociale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4835">numéro d'assurance sociale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4836">numéro de sécu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4836">numéro de sécu</span></span>

## <a name="france-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4838">Налоговый идентификационный номер для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4838">France tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4839">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4839">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4840">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4840">13 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4841">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4841">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4842">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4842">13 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4843">Одна цифра, которая должна быть равна 0, 1, 2 или 3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4843">One digit that must be 0, 1, 2, or 3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4844">1 цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4844">1 digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4845">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4845">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4846">2 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4846">2 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4847">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4847">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4848">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4848">3 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4849">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4849">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4850">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4850">3 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4851">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4851">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4852">3 контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4852">3 check digits</span></span> 

  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4853">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4853">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4854">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4854">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4855">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4855">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4856">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4856">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4857">Функция  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4857">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4858">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4858">A keyword from  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4859">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4859">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4860">Функция  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4860">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- France Tax Identification Number (numéro SPI.) -->
      <Entity id="ed59e77e-171d-442c-9ec1-88e2ebcb5b0a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="france-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4880">Значение налогового номера, добавленного в Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4880">France value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4881">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4881">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4882">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4882">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4883">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4883">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4884">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4884">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4885">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4885">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4886">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4886">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4887">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4887">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4888">13-буквенно-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4888">13 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4889">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4889">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4890">13 символов буквенно-цифрового шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4890">13 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4891">две буквы — FR (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4891">two letters  - FR (case insensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4892">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4892">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4893">две буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4893">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4894">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4894">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4895">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4895">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4896">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4896">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4897">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4897">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4898">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4898">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4899">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4899">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4900">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4900">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4901">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4901">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4902">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4902">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4903">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4903">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4904">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4904">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4905">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4905">A keyword from Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4906">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4906">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4907">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4907">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="949121e6-ad9f-4379-8731-710342baea78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4908">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4908">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_france_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4909">Keyword_France_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4909">Keyword_France_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4912">процент #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4912">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4913">налог на добавленную стоимость</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4913">value added tax</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4914">Siren идентификация No нумéро д'идентификатион таксе Сур валеур ажаутéе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4914">siren identification no numéro d'identification taxe sur valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4915">таксе валеур ажаутéе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4915">taxe valeur ajoutée</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4918">нумéро de тва</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4918">numéro de tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4919">нумéро д'идентификатион Siren</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4919">numéro d'identification siren</span></span>


## <a name="germany-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4920">Номер водительского удостоверения для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4920">Germany driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4921">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4921">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4922">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4922">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4923">сочетание 11 цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4923">combination of 11 digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4924">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4924">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4925">11 цифр и букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4925">11 digits and letters (not case sensitive):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4926">цифра или буква;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4926">a digit or letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4927">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4927">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4928">шесть цифр или букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4928">six digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4929">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4929">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4930">цифра или буква;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4930">a digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4931">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4931">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4932">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4932">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4933">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4933">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4934">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4934">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4935">Функция Func_german_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4935">The function Func_german_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4936">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_german_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4936">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4937">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4937">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="91da9335-1edb-45b7-a95f-5fe41a16c63c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_german_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4938">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4938">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_german_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4939">Keyword_german_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4939">Keyword_german_drivers_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4940">аусстеллунгсдатум</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4940">ausstellungsdatum</span></span>

ausstellende behorde</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4943">ausstellende behorde</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-4945">фüхрерсчеин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-4945">führerschein</span></span>

## <a name="germany-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5086">Номер идентификационной карточки для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5086">Germany identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5087">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5087">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5088">с 1 ноября 2010: девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5088">since 1 November 2010: Nine letters and digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5089">от 1 апреля 1987 до 31 октября 2010:10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5089">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010: 10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5090">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5090">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5091">с 1 ноября 2010:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5091">since 1 November 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5092">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5092">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5093">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5093">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5094">от 1 апреля 1987 до 31 октября 2010:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5094">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5095">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5095">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5096">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5096">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5097">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5097">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5098">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5098">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5099">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5099">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5100">регулярное выражение Regex_germany_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5100">The regular expression Regex_germany_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5101">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_germany_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5101">A keyword from Keyword_germany_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="e577372f-c42e-47a0-9d85-bebed1c237d4" recommendedConfidence="65" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_germany_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_germany_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5102">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5102">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_germany_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5103">Keyword_germany_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5103">Keyword_germany_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5104">аусвеис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5104">ausweis</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5105">гпид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5105">gpid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5106">процедура</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5106">identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5107">идентификатион</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5107">identifikation</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5108">идентифизиерунгснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5108">identifizierungsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5109">идентификационная карточка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5109">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5110">идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5110">identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5111">ID — нуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5111">id-nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5112">личный идентификатор</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5112">personal id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5113">персоналаусвеис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5113">personalausweis</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5114">Идентификатор персöнличе нуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5114">persönliche id nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5115">персöнличе идентификатионснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5115">persönliche identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5116">персöнличе — ID — нуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5116">persönliche-id-nummer</span></span>


## <a name="germany-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5117">Номер паспорта для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5117">Germany passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5118">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5118">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5119">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5119">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5120">десять цифр или букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5120">ten digits or letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5121">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5121">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5122">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5122">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5123">Первый символ — цифра или буква из этого набора (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5123">first character is a digit or a letter from this set (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5124">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5124">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5125">пять цифр или букв из этого набора (C,-H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5125">five digits or letters from this set (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5126">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5126">a digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5127">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5127">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5128">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5128">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5129">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5129">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5130">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5130">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5131">функция Func_german_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5131">The function Func_german_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5132">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keyword_german_passport` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5132">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5133">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5133">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5134">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5134">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5135">функция Func_german_passport_data находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5135">The function Func_german_passport_data finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5136">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keyword_german_passport` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5136">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5137">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5137">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="2e3da144-d42b-47ed-b123-fbf78604e52c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport_data" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5138">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5138">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_german_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5139">Keyword_german_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5139">Keyword_german_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5140">реисепассе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5140">reisepasse</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5141">реисепасснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5141">reisepassnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5142">No-Reisepass</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5142">No-Reisepass</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5143">Nr-Reisepass</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5143">Nr-Reisepass</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5144">Reisepass-Nr</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5144">Reisepass-Nr</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5145">пасснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5145">Passnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5146">реисепäссе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5146">reisepässe</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5147">пассепорт но.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5147">passeport no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5148">пассепорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5148">passeport no</span></span>

## <a name="germany-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5149">Идентификационный номер налогоплательщика (Германия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5149">Germany tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5150">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5150">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5151">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5151">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5152">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5152">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5153">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5153">11 digits :</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5154">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5154">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5155">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5155">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5156">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5156">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5157">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5157">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5158">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5158">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5159">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5159">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5160">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5160">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5161">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5161">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5162">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5162">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5163">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5163">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5164">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5164">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5165">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5165">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5166">Функция  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5166">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5167">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5167">A keyword from  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5168">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5168">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5169">Функция  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5169">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Germany Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="43316a89-9880-40cf-b980-04bc7eefcec5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5195">Значение налогового номера добавленного в Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5195">Germany value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5196">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5196">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5197">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5197">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5198">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5198">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5199">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5199">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5200">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5200">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5201">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5201">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5202">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5202">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5203">11 буквенно-цифрового шаблона</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5203">11 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5204">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5204">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5205">11-буквенно-цифровой буквенно-значный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5205">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5206">буква D или d</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5206">a letter D or d</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5207">буква E или e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5207">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5208">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5208">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5209">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5209">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5210">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5210">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5211">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5211">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5212">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5212">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5213">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5213">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5214">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5214">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5215">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5215">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5216">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5216">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5217">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5217">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5218">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5218">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5219">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5219">A keyword from Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5220">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5220">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5221">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5221">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Germany Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="db177eb2-8811-4842-bffc-128c14aa219f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5222">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5222">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5223">Keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5223">Keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5224">номер НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5224">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5225">НДС No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5225">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5226">процент #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5226">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5227">НДС # мехрвертстеуер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5227">vat#  mehrwertsteuer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5228">мвст</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5228">mwst</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5229">мехрвертстеуер идентификатионснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5229">mehrwertsteuer identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5230">мехрвертстеуер нуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5230">mehrwertsteuer nummer</span></span>


## <a name="greece-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5231">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5231">Greece driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5232">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5232">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5233">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5233">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5234">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5234">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5235">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5235">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5236">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5236">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5237">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5237">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5238">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5238">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5239">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5239">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5240">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5240">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5241">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5241">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5242">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5242">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="7a2200b5-aacf-4e3c-ab36-136d3e68b7da" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5243">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5243">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5251">драйвер Лик</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5251">driver lic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5252">драйвер ликс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5252">driver lics</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5253">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5253">driver license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5254">лицензии на драйверы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5254">driver licenses</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5255">Лицензия на драйвер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5255">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-5256">лицензии на драйверы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-5256">driver licences</span></span>
