## <a name="italy-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6355">Номер паспорта для Италии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6355">Italy passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6356">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6356">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6357">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6357">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6358">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6358">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6359">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6359">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6360">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6360">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6361">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6361">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6362">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6362">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6363">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6363">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6364">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6364">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6365">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6365">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6366">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6366">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6367">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6367">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6368">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6368">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6369">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6369">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number_common"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6370">Keywords_eu_passport_number_common</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6370">Keywords_eu_passport_number_common</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6371">службу #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6371">passport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6372">службу #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6372">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6373">пасспортид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6373">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6374">паспорты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6374">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6375">пасспортно</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6375">passportno</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6376">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6376">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6377">пасспортнумбер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6377">passportnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6378">номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6378">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6379">пасспортнумберс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6379">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6380">номера паспортов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6380">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_italy_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6381">Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6381">Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6382">Итальянский пассапорто</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6382">italiana passaporto</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6383">пассапорто итальянский</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6383">passaporto italiana</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6384">пассапорто нумеро</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6384">passaporto numero</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6385">нумéро пассепорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6385">numéro passeport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6386">Нумеро di пассапорто</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6386">numero di passaporto</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6387">нумери del пассапорто</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6387">numeri del passaporto</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6388">пассепорт италиен</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6388">passeport italien</span></span>

## <a name="italy-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6389">Налоговый номер добавленной стоимости (Италия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6389">Italy value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6390">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6390">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6391">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6391">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6392">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6392">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6393">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6393">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6394">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6394">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6395">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6395">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6396">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6396">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6397">13-буквенно-цифровой буквенный шаблон с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6397">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6398">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6398">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6399">13-буквенно-цифровой буквенно-цифровой шаблон с необязательными ограничителями:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6399">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6400">I или i</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6400">I or i</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6401">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6401">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6402">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6402">optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6403">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6403">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6404">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6404">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6405">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6405">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6406">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6406">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6407">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6407">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6408">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6408">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6409">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6409">A keyword from Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6410">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6410">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6411">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6411">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Italy Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="26a8cc07-2283-4a2a-ab1d-4ab643c4c67f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6412">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6412">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6413">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6413">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6414">номер НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6414">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6415">НДС No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6415">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6416">процент #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6416">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6417">ива</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6417">iva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6418">ива #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6418">iva#</span></span>


## <a name="japan-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6419">Номер банковского счета для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6419">Japan bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6420">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6420">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6421">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6421">seven or eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6422">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6422">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6423">номер банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6423">bank account number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6424">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6424">seven or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6425">код филиала банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6425">bank account branch code:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6426">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6426">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6427">пробел или тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6427">a space or dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6428">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6428">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6429">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6429">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6430">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6430">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6431">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6431">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6432">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6432">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6433">Функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6433">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6434">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6434">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6435">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6435">One of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6436">функция Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6436">The function Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6437">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6437">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6438">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6438">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6439">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6439">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6440">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6440">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="d354f95b-96ee-4b80-80bc-4377312b55bc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Version minEngineVersion="15.01.0131.000">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
  </Version>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6488">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6488">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6489">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6489">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6490">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6490">Pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6492">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6492">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6493">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6493">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6494">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6494">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6495">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6495">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6496">функция Func_jp_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6496">The function Func_jp_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6497">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6497">A keyword from Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="c6011143-d087-451c-8313-7f6d4aed2270" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6536">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6536">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6543">13 цифра, цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6543">13 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6544">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6544">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6545">13 цифра:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6545">13 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6546">одна цифра от 1 до девяти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6546">one digit from one to nine</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6547">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6547">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6548">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6548">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6549">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6549">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6550">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6550">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6551">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6551">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6552">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6552">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6553">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6553">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6554">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6554">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6555">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6555">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Corporate -->
      <Entity id="9e0eaf79-ff20-4ffb-b3e4-e7368d5db6ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6556">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6556">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6558">корпоративный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6558">corporate number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6559">マイナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6559">マイナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6560">共通番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6560">共通番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6561">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6561">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6562">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6562">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6563">個人番号カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6563">個人番号カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6564">個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6564">個人識別番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6565">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6565">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6566">法人番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6566">法人番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6567">指定通知書</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6567">指定通知書</span></span>


## <a name="japan-my-number---personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6568">Япония мой номер — личное</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6568">Japan My Number - Personal</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6569">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6569">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6570">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6570">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6571">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6571">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6572">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6572">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6573">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6573">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6574">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6574">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6575">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6575">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6576">12 цифр номера</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6576">12 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6577">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6577">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6578">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6578">12 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6579">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6579">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6580">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6580">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6581">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6581">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6582">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6582">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6583">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6583">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6584">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6584">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6585">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6585">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6586">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6586">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6587">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6587">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6588">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6588">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6589">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6589">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6590">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6590">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6591">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6591">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Personal -->
      <Entity id="98da8e66-7299-4ebd-9f82-c871ab37d3ef" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6597">共通番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6597">共通番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6598">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6598">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6599">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6599">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6600">個人番号カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6600">個人番号カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6601">個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6601">個人識別番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6602">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6602">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>

## <a name="japan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6604">Номер паспорта для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6604">Japan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6605">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6605">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6606">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6606">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6607">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6607">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6608">две буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6608">two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6609">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6609">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6610">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6610">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6611">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6611">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6612">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6612">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6613">функция Func_jp_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6613">The function Func_jp_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6614">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6614">A keyword from Keyword_jp_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="75177310-1a09-4613-bf6d-833aae3743f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6615">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6615">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6619">Паспорт No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6619">Passport No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6620">Passport#
</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6620">Passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6621">パスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6621">パスポート</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6622">パスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6622">パスポート番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6623">パスポートナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6623">パスポートナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6624">パスポート #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6624">パスポート＃</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6625">パスポート #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6625">パスポート#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6626">パスポートно.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6626">パスポートNo.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6627">旅券番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6627">旅券番号</span></span>

## <a name="japan-residence-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6631">Номер карточки для Японии (Япония)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6631">Japan residence card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6632">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6632">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6633">12 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6633">12 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6634">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6634">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6635">12 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6635">12 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6636">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6636">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6637">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6637">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6638">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6638">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6639">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6639">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6640">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6640">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6641">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6641">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6642">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6642">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6643">Регулярное выражение Regex_jp_residence_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6643">The regular expression Regex_jp_residence_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6644">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_residence_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6644">A keyword from Keyword_jp_residence_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Japan Residence Card Number-->
-<Entity id="ac36fef2-a289-4e2c-bb48-b02366e89fc0" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_jp_residence_card_number"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_residence_card_number"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6645">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6645">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_residence_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6646">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6646">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6647">Номер карточки проживания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6647">Residence card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6648">Номер карточки проживания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6648">Residence card no</span></span>

## <a name="japan-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6653">Номер резидентного регистрационного номера для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6653">Japan resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6654">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6654">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6655">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6655">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6656">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6656">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6657">11 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6657">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6658">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6658">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6659">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6659">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6660">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6660">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6661">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6661">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6662">функция Func_jp_resident_registration_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6662">The function Func_jp_resident_registration_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6663">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6663">A keyword from Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="01c1209b-6389-4faf-a5f8-3f7e13899652" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_resident_registration_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6664">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6664">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_resident_registration_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6665">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6665">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6666">Resident Registration Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6666">Resident Registration Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6667">Residents Basic Registry Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6667">Residents Basic Registry Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6668">Resident Registration No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6668">Resident Registration No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6669">Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6669">Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6670">Residents Basic Registry No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6670">Residents Basic Registry No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6671">Basic Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6671">Basic Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6672">外国人登録証明書番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6672">外国人登録証明書番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6673">証明書番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6673">証明書番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6674">登録番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6674">登録番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6675">外国人登録証</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6675">外国人登録証</span></span>

   
## <a name="japan-social-insurance-number-sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6676">Номер социального страхования для Японии (SIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6676">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6677">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6677">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6678">7–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6678">7-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6679">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6679">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6680">7–12 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6680">7-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6681">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6681">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6682">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6682">a hyphen (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6683">шесть цифр или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6683">six digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6684">7–12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6684">7-12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6685">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6685">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6686">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6686">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6687">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6687">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6688">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6688">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6689">функция Func_jp_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6689">The function Func_jp_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6690">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6690">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6691">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6691">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6692">функция Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6692">The function Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6693">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6693">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="c840e719-0896-45bb-84fd-1ed5c95e45ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin_pre_1997" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_jp_sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6695">Keyword_jp_sin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6695">Keyword_jp_sin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6696">Social Insurance No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6696">Social Insurance No.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6701">基礎年金番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6701">基礎年金番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6702">雇用保険被保険者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6702">雇用保険被保険者番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6703">雇用保険番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6703">雇用保険番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6704">保険証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6704">保険証番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6705">社会保険番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6705">社会保険番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6706">社会保険но.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6706">社会保険No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6707">社会保険</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6707">社会保険</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6708">介護保険</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6708">介護保険</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6709">介護保険被保険者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6709">介護保険被保険者番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6710">健康保険被保険者整理番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6710">健康保険被保険者整理番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6711">雇用保険被保険者整理番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6711">雇用保険被保険者整理番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6712">厚生年金</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6712">厚生年金</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6713">厚生年金被保険者整理番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6713">厚生年金被保険者整理番号</span></span>


## <a name="latvia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6714">Номер водительского удостоверения для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6714">Latvia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6715">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6715">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6716">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6716">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6717">три буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6717">three letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6718">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6718">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6719">три буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6719">three letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6720">три буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6720">three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6721">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6721">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6722">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6722">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6723">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6723">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6724">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6724">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6725">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6725">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6726">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6726">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6727">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6727">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="ec996de0-30f2-46b1-b192-4d2ff8805fa7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6728">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6728">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6729">Keywords_eu_driver "s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6729">Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6730">дриверлик</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6730">driverlic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6731">дриверликс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6731">driverlics</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6732">дриверлиценсе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6732">driverlicense</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6854">11 цифр и необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6854">11 digits and an optional hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6855">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6855">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6856">Старый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6856">Old format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6857">11 цифр и дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6857">11 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6858">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММГГ —)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6858">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6859">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6859">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6860">одна цифра, соответствующая столетию рождения ("0" для 19 века, "1" для 20-й век) и "2" для 21 века)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6860">one digit that corresponds to the century of birth ("0" for 19th century, "1" for 20th century, and "2" for 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6861">четыре цифры, созданные случайным образом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6861">four digits, randomly generated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6862">Новый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6862">New format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6863">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6863">11 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6864">Две цифры "32"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6864">Two digits "32"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6865">девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6865">Nine digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6866">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6866">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6867">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6867">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6868">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6868">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6869">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6869">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6870">Функция  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` или регулярное выражение `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` выполняет поиск содержимого, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6870">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6871">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6871">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6872">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6872">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6873">Функция  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` или регулярное выражение `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` выполняет поиск содержимого, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6873">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="03fcf763-27c2-49ed-9422-2641c6c895c9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="latvia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6936">Номер паспорта для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6936">Latvia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6937">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6937">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6938">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6938">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6939">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6939">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6940">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6940">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6941">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6941">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6942">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6942">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6943">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6943">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6944">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6944">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6945">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6945">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6946">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6946">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6947">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6947">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6948">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6948">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6949">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6949">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
```

## <a name="lithuania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6969">Литва номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6969">Lithuania driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6970">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6970">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6971">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6971">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6972">восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6972">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6973">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6973">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6974">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6974">eight digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6975">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6975">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6976">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6976">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6977">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6977">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6978">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6978">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6979">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6979">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-6980">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-6980">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="86f7628b-e0f4-4dc3-9fbc-e4300e4c7d78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7105">Литва персональный код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7105">Lithuania personal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7106">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7106">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7107">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7107">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7108">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7108">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7109">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7109">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7110">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7110">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7111">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7111">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7112">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7112">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7113">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7113">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7114">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7114">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7115">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7115">11 digits without spaces and delimiters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7116">одна цифра (1-6), соответствующая пол и век рождения человека</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7116">one digit (1-6) that corresponds to the person's gender and century of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7117">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7117">six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7118">три цифры, которые соответствуют серийному числу даты рождения.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7118">three digits that correspond to the serial number of the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7119">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7119">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7120">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7120">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7121">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7121">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7122">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7122">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7123">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7123">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7124">Функция  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7124">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7125">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7125">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7126">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7126">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7127">Функция  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7127">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="cd6d3786-8ec3-4524-a2cf-1e0095379171" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7162">Литва номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7162">Lithuania passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7163">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7163">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7164">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7164">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7165">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7165">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7166">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7166">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7167">восемь цифр или букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7167">eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7168">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7168">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7169">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7169">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7170">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7170">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7171">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7171">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7172">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7172">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7173">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7173">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7190">Номер водительского удостоверения Луксембург</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7190">Luxemburg driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7191">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7191">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7192">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7192">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7193">шесть цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7193">six digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7194">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7194">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7195">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7195">six digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7196">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7196">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7197">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7197">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7198">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7198">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7199">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7199">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7200">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7200">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-7201">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-7201">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="89daf717-1544-4860-9a2e-fc9166dd8852" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
