## <a name="new-zealand-ministry-of-health-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8189">Номер министерства здоровья Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8189">New Zealand ministry of health number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8190">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8190">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8191">три буквы, пробел (необязательно) и четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8191">three letters, a space (optional), and four digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8192">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8192">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8193">три буквы (без учета регистра), пробел (необязательно) из четырех цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8193">three letters (not case sensitive) a space (optional) four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8194">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8194">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8195">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8195">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8196">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8196">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8197">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8197">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8198">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8198">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8199">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_nz_terms;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8199">A keyword from Keyword_nz_terms is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8200">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8200">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- New Zealand Health Number -->
<Entity id="2b71c1c8-d14e-4430-82dc-fd1ed6bf05c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_nz_terms" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8201">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8201">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_nz_terms"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8202">Keyword_nz_terms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8202">Keyword_nz_terms</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8203">нхи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8203">NHI</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8204">Новая Зеландия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8204">New Zealand</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8205">Здравоохранение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8205">Health</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8206">обращения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8206">treatment</span></span> 


## <a name="new-zealand-social-wlefare-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8207">Номер социального влефареа Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8207">New Zealand social wlefare number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8208">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8208">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8209">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8209">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8210">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8210">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8211">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8211">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8212">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8212">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8213">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8213">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8214">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8214">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8215">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8215">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8216">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8216">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8217">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8217">nine digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8218">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8218">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8219">Необязательный перенос</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8219">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8220">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8220">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8221">Необязательный перенос</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8221">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8222">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8222">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8223">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8223">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8224">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8224">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8225">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8225">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8226">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8226">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8227">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8227">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8228">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8228">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8229">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8229">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8230">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8230">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Newzealand Social Welfare Number -->
      <Entity id="20f3c48d-4ac1-4cd2-86bd-34ecc1826e9d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8231">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8231">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8232">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8232">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8233">социальные велфаре #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8233">social welfare #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8234">социальные велфаре #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8234">social welfare#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8235">социальное велфаре No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8235">social welfare No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8236">номер социального велфаре</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8236">social welfare number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8237">свн #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8237">swn#</span></span>

   
## <a name="norway-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8238">Идентификационный номер Норвегии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8238">Norway identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8239">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8239">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8240">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8240">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8241">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8241">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8242">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8242">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8243">шесть цифр в формате ддммгг — Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8243">six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8244">индивидуальный номер из трех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8244">three-digit individual number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8245">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8245">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8246">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8246">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8247">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8247">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8248">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8248">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8249">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8249">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8250">функция Func_norway_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8250">The function Func_norway_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8251">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_norway_id_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8251">A keyword from Keyword_norway_id_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8252">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8252">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8253">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8253">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8254">функция Func_norway_id_numbe находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8254">The function Func_norway_id_numbe finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8255">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8255">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Norway Identification Number -->
<Entity id="d4c8a798-e9f2-4bd3-9652-500d24080fc3" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8256">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8256">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_norway_id_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8257">Keyword_norway_id_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8257">Keyword_norway_id_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8258">Personal identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8258">Personal identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8259">Norwegian ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8259">Norwegian ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8260">ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8260">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8261">Процедура</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8261">Identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8262">персоннуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8262">Personnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8263">фøдселснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8263">Fødselsnummer</span></span>

   
## <a name="philippines-unified-multi-purpose-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8264">Идентификационный номер единой системы для различных целей Филиппины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8264">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8265">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8265">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8266">12 цифр, разделенных дефисами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8266">12 digits separated by hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8267">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8267">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8268">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8268">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8269">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8269">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8270">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8270">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8271">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8271">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8272">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8272">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8273">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8273">one digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8274">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8274">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8275">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8275">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8276">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8276">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8277">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8277">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8278">регулярное выражение Regex_philippines_unified_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8278">The regular expression Regex_philippines_unified_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8279">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_philippines_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8279">A keyword from Keyword_philippines_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Philippines Unified Multi-Purpose ID number -->
<Entity id="019b39dd-8c25-4765-91a3-d9c6baf3c3b3" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_philippines_unified_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_philippines_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8280">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8280">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_philippines_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8281">Keyword_philippines_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8281">Keyword_philippines_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8282">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8282">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8283">умид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8283">UMID</span></span>

## <a name="poland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8286">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8286">Poland driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8287">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8287">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8288">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8288">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8289">14 цифр, содержащих 2 косых черты.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8289">14 digits containing 2 forward slashes</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8290">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8290">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8291">14 цифр и 2 косых черт:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8291">14 digits and 2 forward slashes:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8292">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8292">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8293">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8293">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8294">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8294">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8295">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8295">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8296">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8296">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8297">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8297">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8298">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8298">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8299">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8299">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8300">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8300">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8301">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8301">The regular expression  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8302">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8302">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Poland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="24d51f99-ee9e-4060-a077-cae58cab1ee4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8426">Идентификационная карточка Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8426">Poland identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8427">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8427">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8428">три буквы и шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8428">three letters and six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8429">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8429">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8430">три буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8430">three letters (not case sensitive) followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8431">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8431">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8432">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8432">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8433">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8433">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8434">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8434">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8435">функция Func_polish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8435">The function Func_polish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8436">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8436">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8437">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8437">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Identity Card-->
<Entity id="25E64989-ED5D-40CA-A939-6C14183BB7BF" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8438">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8438">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8439">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8439">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8440">Довóд особисти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8440">Dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8441">Нумер доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8441">Numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8442">Назва i нумер доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8442">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8443">Назва i НР доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8443">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8444">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8444">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8445">Dowód Tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8445">Dowód Tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8446">Dow.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8446">dow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8447">совместим.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8447">os.</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-national-id-pesel"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8448">Национальный идентификатор Польша (PESEL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8448">Poland national ID (PESEL)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8449">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8449">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8450">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8450">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8451">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8451">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8452">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения, в формате ГГММДД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8452">6 digits representing date of birth in the format YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8453">4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8453">4 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8454">1 контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8454">1 check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8455">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8455">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8456">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8456">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8457">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8457">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8458">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8458">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8459">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8459">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8460">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_pesel_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8460">A keyword from Keyword_pesel_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8461">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8461">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8462">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8462">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8463">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8463">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8464">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8464">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland National ID (PESEL) -->
      <Entity id="E3AAF206-4297-412F-9E06-BA8487E22456" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8465">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8465">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8470">ниеповтарзалнинумер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8470">niepowtarzalnynumer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8471">НР. PESEL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8471">nr.-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8472">НР — PESEL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8472">nr-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8473">Нумер идентификацижни</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8473">numer identyfikacyjny</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8474">PESEL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8474">pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8475">тоżсамоśЦи народовеж</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8475">tożsamości narodowej</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8476">Номер паспорта для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8476">Poland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8477">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8477">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8478">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8478">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8479">две буквы и семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8479">two letters and seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8480">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8480">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8481">Две буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8481">Two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8482">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8482">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8483">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8483">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8484">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8484">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8485">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8485">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8486">функция Func_polish_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8486">The function Func_polish_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8487">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8487">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8488">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8488">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Passport Number -->
<Entity id="03937FB5-D2B6-4487-B61F-0F8BFF7C3517" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
</Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8489">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8489">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8490">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8490">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8491">Нумер пасзпорту</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8491">Numer paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8492">НР.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8492">Nr.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8493">пасзпорту</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8493">Paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8494">пасзпорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8494">Paszport</span></span>

## <a name="poland-regon-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8495">Номер РЕГОНа Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8495">Poland REGON number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8496">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8496">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8497">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8497">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8498">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8498">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8499">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8499">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8500">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8500">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8501">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8501">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8502">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8502">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8503">девять цифр или номер из 14 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8503">nine digit or 14 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8504">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8504">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8505">девять цифр или 14 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8505">nine digit or 14-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8506">девять цифр или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8506">nine digits or</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8507">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8507">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8508">дискрецион</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8508">hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8509">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8509">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8510">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8510">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8511">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8511">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8512">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8512">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8513">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8513">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8514">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8514">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8515">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_polish_regon_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8515">A keyword from Keywords_polish_regon_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8516">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8516">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8517">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8517">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Polish REGON Number  -->
      <Entity id="fc87b421-f437-4f8b-b739-29a735ead0d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8518">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8518">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_poland_regon_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8519">Keywords_poland_regon_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8519">Keywords_poland_regon_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8520">Идентификатор РЕГОН</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8520">regon id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8521">Статистический номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8521">statistical number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8522">Идентификатор статистики</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8522">statistical id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8523">Статистическая нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8523">statistical no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8524">номер РЕГОН</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8524">regon number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8525">регонид #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8525">regonid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8526">регонно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8526">regonno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8527">Код компании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8527">company id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8528">компанид #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8528">companyid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8529">компанидно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8529">companyidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8530">Нумер статистикзни</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8530">numer statystyczny</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8531">нумеру РЕГОН</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8531">numeru regon</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8532">нумерстатистикзни #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8532">numerstatystyczny#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8533">нумерурегон #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8533">numeruregon#</span></span>


## <a name="poland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8534">Идентификационный номер для таможенного учета Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8534">Poland tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8535">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8535">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8536">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8536">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8537">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8537">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8538">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8538">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8539">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8539">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8540">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8540">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8541">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8541">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8542">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8542">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8543">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8543">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8544">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8544">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8545">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8545">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8546">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8546">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8547">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8547">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8548">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8548">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8549">Функция  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8549">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8550">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8550">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
  
```xml
      <!-- Poland Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="1ff28b4d-40f2-49e9-b677-9606a88e2bca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8551">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8551">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8560">налог без #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8560">tax no#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8567">таксно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8567">taxno#</span></span>

## <a name="portugal-citizen-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8580">Номер карточки с префиксом "Португалия"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8580">Portugal citizen card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8581">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8581">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8582">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8582">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8583">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8583">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8584">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8584">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8585">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8585">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8586">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8586">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8587">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8587">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8588">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8588">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8589">регулярное выражение Regex_portugal_citizen_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8589">The regular expression Regex_portugal_citizen_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8590">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_portugal_citizen_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8590">A keyword from Keyword_portugal_citizen_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Portugal Citizen Card Number -->
<Entity id="91a7ece2-add4-4986-9a15-c84544d81ecd" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_citizen_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_portugal_citizen_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8591">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8591">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="portugal-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8610">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8610">Portugal driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8611">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8611">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8612">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8612">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8613">два образца — две буквы, за которыми следуют 5-8 цифр со специальными символами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8613">two patterns - two letters followed by 5-8 digits with special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8614">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8614">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8615">Pattern 1: две буквы, за которыми следует 5/6 со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8615">Pattern 1: Two letters followed by 5/6 with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8616">Две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8616">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8617">дефис;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8617">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8618">Пять или шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8618">Five or Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8619">Пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8619">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8620">Одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8620">One digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8621">Шаблон 2: одна буква, за которой следуют 6/8 цифры со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8621">Pattern 2: One letter followed by 6/8 digits with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8622">Одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8622">One letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8623">дефис;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8623">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8624">Шесть или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8624">Six or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8625">Пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8625">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8626">одна цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8626">One digit</span></span>

    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8627">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8627">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8628">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8628">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8629">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8629">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8630">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8630">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8631">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8631">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8632">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8632">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="977f1e5a-2c33-4bcc-b516-95bb275cff23" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8764">Номер паспорта для Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8764">Portugal passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8765">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8765">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8766">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8766">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8767">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8767">one letter followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8768">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8768">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8769">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8769">one letter followed by six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8770">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8770">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8771">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8771">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8772">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8772">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8773">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8773">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8774">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8774">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8775">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8775">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8776">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8776">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8777">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8777">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8801">Идентификационный номер для налога на Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8801">Portugal tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8802">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8802">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8803">девять цифр с необязательными пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8803">nine digits with optional spaces</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8804">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8804">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8805">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8805">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8806">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8806">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8807">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8807">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8808">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8808">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8809">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8809">3 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8810">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8810">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8811">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8811">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8812">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8812">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8813">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8813">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8814">Функция  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8814">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8815">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8815">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8816">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8816">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8817">Функция  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8817">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="65372402-3131-4f1e-9983-4439841d1f15" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8842">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Румыния</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8842">Romania driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8843">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8843">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8844">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8844">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8845">один символ, за которым следуют восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8845">one character followed by eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8846">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8846">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8847">один символ, за которым следуют восемь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8847">one character followed by eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8848">одна буква (без учета регистра) или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8848">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8849">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8849">eight digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8850">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8850">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8851">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8851">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8852">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8852">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8853">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8853">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8854">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8854">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8855">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8855">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="b5511ace-2fd8-4ae4-b6fc-c7c6e4689e3c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-personal-numeric-code-cnp"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8983">Персональный числовой код Румыния (КНП)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8983">Romania personal numeric code (CNP)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8984">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8984">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8985">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8985">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8986">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8986">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8987">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8987">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8988">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8988">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8989">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8989">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8990">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8990">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8991">13 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8991">13 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8992">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8992">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8993">1 цифра из 1-9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8993">1 digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8994">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8994">6 digits representing date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8995">2 цифры, которые могут быть 01-52 или 99</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8995">2 digits which can be 01-52 or 99</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8996">4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8996">4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8997">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8997">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8998">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8998">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-8999">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-8999">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9000">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9000">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9001">Функция  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9001">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9002">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9002">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9003">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9003">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9004">Функция  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9004">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Personal Numerical Code (CNP) -->
      <Entity id="eb5fa399-fe28-4c67-8188-d63a616ed89c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9055">Номер паспорта для Румыния</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9055">Romania passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9056">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9056">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9057">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9057">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9058">восемь или девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9058">eight or nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9059">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9059">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9060">восемь или девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9060">eight or nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9061">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9061">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9062">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9062">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9063">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9063">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9064">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9064">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9065">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9065">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9066">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9066">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_romania_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9079">Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9079">Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9080">нумăрул паșапортулуи нумарул пасапортулуи нумереле паșапортулуи паșапорт НР</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9080">numărul pașaportului numarul pasaportului numerele pașaportului Pașaport nr</span></span>

## <a name="russia-passport-number-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9081">Номер паспорта для России (Россия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9081">Russia passport number domestic</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9082">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9082">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9083">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9083">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9084">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9084">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9085">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9085">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9086">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9086">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9087">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9087">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9088">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9088">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9089">номер из десяти цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9089">ten digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9090">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9090">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9091">номер из десяти цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9091">ten digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9092">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9092">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9093">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9093">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9094">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9094">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9095">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9095">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9096">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9096">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9097">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9097">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9098">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9098">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9099">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9099">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9100">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9100">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9101">Регулярное выражение Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9101">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9102">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9102">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number Domestic -->
      <Entity id="76ec2f5d-cedb-48e1-8070-1998794af445" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
