## <a name="russia-passport-number-international"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9119">Номер паспорта для России Международная</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9119">Russia passport number international</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9120">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9120">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9123">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9123">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9124">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9124">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9125">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9125">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9126">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9126">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9127">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9127">nine digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9128">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9128">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9129">девять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9129">nine digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9130">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9130">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9131">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9131">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9132">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9132">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9133">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9133">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9134">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9134">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9135">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9135">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9136">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9136">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9137">Регулярное выражение Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9137">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9138">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9138">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number International -->
      <Entity id="ac5f4878-75e4-4b82-af2d-02e13ea9f411" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9139">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9139">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_russia_passport_number_international"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9140">Keywords_russia_passport_number_international</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9140">Keywords_russia_passport_number_international</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9141">номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9141">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9142">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9142">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9143">службу #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9143">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9144">идентификатор паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9144">passport id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9145">пасспортно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9145">passportno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9146">пасспортнумбер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9146">passportnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9147">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9147">паспорт нет</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9148">Идентификатор паспорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9148">паспорт id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9149">поссийской паспорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9149">pоссийской паспорт</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9150">пусский номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9150">pусский номер паспорта</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9151">паспорт #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9151">паспорт#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9152">паспортид #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9152">паспортid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9153">номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9153">номер паспорта</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9154">номерпаспорта #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9154">номерпаспорта#</span></span>


## <a name="saudi-arabia-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9155">Национальный идентификатор для Саудовской Аравии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9155">Saudi Arabia National ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9156">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9156">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9157">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9157">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9158">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9158">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9159">десять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9159">ten consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9160">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9160">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9161">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9161">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9162">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9162">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9163">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9163">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9164">регулярное выражение Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9164">The regular expression Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9165">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9165">A keyword from Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Saudi Arabia National ID -->
<Entity id="8c5a0ba8-404a-41a3-8871-746aa21ee6c0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9166">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9166">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9167">Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9167">Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9168">Identification Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9168">Identification Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9169">I card number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9169">I card number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9170">ID number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9170">ID number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9171">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9171">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span></span> 

   
## <a name="singapore-national-registration-identity-card-nric-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9172">Номер национальной идентификационной карточки для регистрации (NRIC), Сингапур</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9172">Singapore national registration identity card (NRIC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9173">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9173">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9174">девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9174">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9175">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9175">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9176">девять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9176">nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9177">буква "F", "G", "S" или "T" (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9177">the letter "F", "G", "S", or "T" (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9178">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9178">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9179">цифра алфавитной проверки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9179">an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9180">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9180">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9181">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9181">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9182">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9182">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9183">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9183">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9184">регулярное выражение Regex_singapore_nric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9184">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9185">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_singapore_nric;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9185">A keyword from Keyword_singapore_nric is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9186">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9186">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9187">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9187">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9188">регулярное выражение Regex_singapore_nric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9188">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9189">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9189">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Singapore National Registration Identity Card (NRIC) Number -->
<Entity id="cead390a-dd83-4856-9751-fb6dc98c34da" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9190">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9190">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_singapore_nric"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9191">Keyword_singapore_nric</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9191">Keyword_singapore_nric</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9192">National Registration Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9192">National Registration Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9193">Identity Card Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9193">Identity Card Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9194">NRIC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9194">NRIC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9195">ВНУТРЕННИХ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9195">IC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9196">Foreign Identification Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9196">Foreign Identification Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9197">ПРОЦЕНТ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9197">FIN</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9198">身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9198">身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9199">身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9199">身份證</span></span> 

## <a name="slovakia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9200">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Словакия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9200">Slovakia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9201">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9201">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9202">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9202">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9203">один символ, за которым следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9203">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9204">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9204">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9205">один символ, за которым следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9205">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9206">одна буква (без учета регистра) или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9206">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9207">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9207">seven digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9208">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9208">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9209">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9209">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9210">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9210">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9211">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9211">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9212">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9212">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9213">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9213">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="14240c22-b6de-4ce5-a90b-137f74252513" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9214">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9214">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9215">Keywords_eu_driver "s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9215">Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9337">водиčскéхо преуказу</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9337">vodičského preukazu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9338">водиčскýч преуказов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9338">vodičských preukazov</span></span>

## <a name="slovakia-personal-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9339">Словакия персональный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9339">Slovakia personal number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9340">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9340">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9341">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9341">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9342">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9342">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9343">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9343">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9344">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9344">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9345">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9345">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9346">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9346">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9347">девять или десять цифр, содержащих необязательную обратную косую черту</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9347">nine or ten digits containing optional backslash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9348">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9348">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9349">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9349">6 digits representing date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9350">Необязательная косая черта (/)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9350">optional slash (/)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9351">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9351">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9352">1 обязательная контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9352">1 optional check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9353">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9353">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9354">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9354">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9355">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9355">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9356">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9356">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9357">Функция  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9357">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9358">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9358">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9359">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9359">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9360">Функция  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9360">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Personal Number -->
      <Entity id="951c26b7-3b35-4f73-924b-15dd599cb9ab" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

## <a name="slovakia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9407">Словакия — номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9407">Slovakia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9408">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9408">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9409">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9409">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9410">одна цифра или буква, за которой следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9410">one digit or letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9411">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9411">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9412">одна цифра или буква (без учета регистра), за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9412">one digit or letter (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9413">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9413">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9414">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9414">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9415">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9415">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9416">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9416">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9417">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9417">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9418">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9418">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9419">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9419">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9431">Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9431">Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9432">číсло Пасу</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9432">číslo pasu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9433">číсла пасов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9433">čísla pasov</span></span>

## <a name="slovenia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9437">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Словения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9437">Slovenia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9438">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9438">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9439">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9439">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9440">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9440">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9441">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9441">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9442">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9442">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9443">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9443">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9444">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9444">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9445">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9445">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9446">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9446">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9447">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9447">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9448">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9448">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5bc089a-f2ee-433d-a6b1-5c253051d6f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-unique-master-citizen-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9575">Словения уникальный номер хозяина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9575">Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9576">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9576">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9577">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9577">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9578">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9578">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9579">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9579">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9580">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9580">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9581">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9581">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9582">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9582">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9583">13 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9583">13 digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9584">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9584">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9585">13 цифр в указанном шаблоне:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9585">13 digits in the specified pattern:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9586">семь цифр, которые соответствуют дате рождения (ДДММЛЛЛ), где "ЛЛЛ" соответствует последним трем цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9586">seven digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMLLL) where "LLL" corresponds to the last three digits of the birth year</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9587">две цифры, соответствующие области рождения "50"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9587">two digits that correspond to the area of birth "50"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9588">три цифры, которые соответствуют сочетанию пола и серийного номера для людей, которые приставили один и тот же день (000-499 для пола и 500-999 для розетки)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9588">three digits that correspond to a combination of gender and serial number for persons born on the same day (000-499 for male and 500-999 for female)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9589">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9589">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9590">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9590">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9591">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9591">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9592">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9592">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9593">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9593">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9594">Функция  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9594">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9595">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9595">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9596">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9596">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9597">Функция  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9597">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number -->
      <Entity id="68948b27-803d-41e4-adf1-13e05eb541bb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9625">Номер паспорта для Словения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9625">Slovenia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9626">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9626">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9627">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9627">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9628">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9628">two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9629">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9629">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9630">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9630">two letters followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9631">буква "P"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9631">the letter "P"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9632">одна прописная буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9632">one uppercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9633">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9633">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9634">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9634">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9635">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9635">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9636">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9636">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9637">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9637">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9638">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9638">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9639">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9639">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9640">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9640">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number_common"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9641">Keywords_eu_passport_number_common</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9641">Keywords_eu_passport_number_common</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9642">службу #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9642">passport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9643">службу #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9643">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9644">пасспортид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9644">passportid</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9648">пасспортнумбер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9648">passportnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9649">номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9649">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9650">пасспортнумберс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9650">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9651">номера паспортов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9651">passport numbers</span></span>

## <a name="slovenia-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9659">Идентификационный номер для налога на Словения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9659">Slovenia tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9660">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9660">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9661">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9661">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9662">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9662">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9663">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9663">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9664">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9664">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9665">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9665">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9666">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9666">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9667">восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9667">eight digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9668">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9668">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9669">одна цифра из 1-9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9669">one digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9670">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9670">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9671">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9671">one check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9672">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9672">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9673">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9673">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9674">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9674">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9675">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9675">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9676">Функция  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9676">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9677">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9677">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9678">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9678">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9679">Функция  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9679">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="e47b071e-c352-4d70-8241-8c215ad65505" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9680">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9680">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9681">Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9681">Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9683">идентификаЦижска šтевилка Давка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9683">identifikacijska številka davka</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9684">šтевилка давčне датотеке</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9684">številka davčne datoteke</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9685">Налоговый файл нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9685">tax file no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9686">номер налогового файла</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9686">tax file number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9688">Налоговый идентификатор</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9688">tax identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9689">идентификационный номер налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9689">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9690">налог без #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9690">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9691">налог без</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9691">tax no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9692">Налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9692">tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9693">Регистрационный номер налогоплательщика</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9693">tax registration number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9694">такси #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9694">taxid#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9696">таксиднумбер #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9696">taxidnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9697">таксно #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9697">taxno#</span></span>

## <a name="south-africa-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9703">Идентификационный номер Южно-Африканского Республика</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9703">South Africa identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9704">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9704">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9705">13 цифр, которые могут содержать пробелы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9705">13 digits that may contain spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9706">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9706">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9707">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9707">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9708">шесть цифр в формате ГГММДД Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9708">six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9709">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9709">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9710">Индикатор гражданства, состоящих из одной цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9710">a single-digit citizenship indicator</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9711">цифра "8" или "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9711">the digit "8" or "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9712">одна цифра контрольной суммы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9712">one digit which is a checksum digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9713">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9713">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9714">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9714">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9715">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9715">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9716">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9716">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9717">функция Func_south_africa_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9717">The function Func_south_africa_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9718">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_south_africa_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9718">A keyword from Keyword_south_africa_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9719">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9719">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Africa Identification Number -->
<Entity id="e2adf7cb-8ea6-4048-a2ed-d89eb65f2780" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_africa_identification_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_africa_identification_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9720">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9720">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_south_africa_identification_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9721">Keyword_south_africa_identification_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9721">Keyword_south_africa_identification_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9722">Identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9722">Identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9723">ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9723">ID</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9724">Процедура</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9724">Identification</span></span> 
   
## <a name="south-korea-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9725">Регистрационный номер резидентной Южной Кореи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9725">South Korea resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9726">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9726">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9727">13 цифр, содержащих дефис.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9727">13 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9728">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9728">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9729">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9729">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9730">шесть цифр в формате ГГММДД Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9730">six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9731">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9731">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9732">одна цифра, определяемая столетием и пол</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9732">one digit determined by the century and gender</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9733">код региона рождения из четырех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9733">four-digit region-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9734">одна цифра, используемая для различения людей, для которых предыдущие числа идентичны</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9734">one digit used to differentiate people for whom the preceding numbers are identical</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9735">контрольная цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9735">a check digit.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9736">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9736">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9737">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9737">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9738">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9738">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9739">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9739">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9740">функция Func_south_korea_resident_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9740">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9741">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_south_korea_resident_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9741">A keyword from Keyword_south_korea_resident_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9742">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9742">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9743">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9743">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9744">функция Func_south_korea_resident_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9744">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9745">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9745">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Korea Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="5b802e18-ba80-44c4-bc83-bf2ad36ae36a" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9746">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9746">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_south_korea_resident_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9747">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9747">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9748">National ID card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9748">National ID card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9749">Citizen's Registration Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9749">Citizen's Registration Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9750">Jumin deungnok beonho</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9750">Jumin deungnok beonho</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9751">ррн</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9751">RRN</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9752">주민등록번호</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9752">주민등록번호</span></span>

## <a name="spain-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9753">Номер водительского удостоверения для Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9753">Spain driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9754">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9754">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9755">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9755">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9756">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9756">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9757">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9757">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9758">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9758">eight digits followed by one character:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9759">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9759">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9760">одна цифра или буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9760">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9761">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9761">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9762">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9762">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9763">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9763">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9764">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9764">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9765">Функция  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` или `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9765">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9766">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9766">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9767">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9767">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9768">Функция  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` или `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9768">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5a82922-b501-4f40-8868-341321146aa2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-dni"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9902">Испания, DNI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9902">Spain DNI</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9903">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9903">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9904">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9904">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9905">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9905">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9906">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9906">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9907">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9907">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9908">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9908">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9909">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9909">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9910">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9910">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9911">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9911">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9912">семь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9912">seven digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9913">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9913">eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9914">Необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9914">An optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9915">один проверочный символ (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9915">one check letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9916">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9916">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9917">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9917">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9918">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9918">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9919">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9919">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9920">Функция  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` или `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9920">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9921">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9921">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9922">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9922">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d2e4b-9923">Функция  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` или `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d2e4b-9923">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

    
```xml
      <!-- Spain DNI -->
      <Entity id="8e6251b9-47b4-40e8-a42b-0f80876be192" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
